  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0baa\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0, \u0bb7\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba9 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf, \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95 \u0b86\u0bb2\u0bcb\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Appointment of Professors Sunanda Mathumabandara and Shenuka Senaviratne as National and International Media Advisers to the President",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prof. Sunanda Mathumabandara and Prof. Shenuka Senaviratne have been appointed as National and International Media Advisers to the President. These appointments have been made by President's Office of the President, Secretary to the President Saman Ekanayake.",
        "Professor Sunanda Mathumabandara recently assumed duties as Senior Advisor to the President (Media) and Professor Shenuka Senaviratne as Senior Advisor to the President (International Media).",
        "Professor Sunanda Mathumabandara, former Vice-Chancellor of Kelani University, has served as the Head of the Department of Economics and the Dean of the Faculty of Social Sciences.",
        "He has served as Secretary of the State Ministry of Mass Media, Director General of Government Information Department and Director General of Development and Communication of the Ministry of Economic Development.",
        "Senior Adviser (International Media) to the President, Shenuka Senaviratne, is a senior officer with extensive experience in diplomatic affairs of this country, who has also held the post of Secretary to the Ministry of External Affairs.",
        "Shenuka Senaviratne has served as Sri Lankan High Commissioner to the United Kingdom, Sri Lankan Ambassador to Thailand, and Permanent Representative to the United Nations in Geneva and New York."
      ],
